						               													<description>Chef de bataillon introduces you to the exciting world of tactical warfare in the Napoleonic period. Especially designed for use with historical miniatures, Chef de bataillon places you in command of the units of history&amp;rsquo;s most colorful and heroic era. You are the Chef de bataillon, in command of a infantry battalion, cavalry regiment, or a battery of artillery.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Battalion and regimental officers, as well as command personalities are incorporated into Chef de bataillon&amp;rsquo;s unique rules system. Battles may be played with miniatures in any range from 5mm to 25mm. Chef de bataillon is so flexible it allows you to play tactical level battles throughout the entire horse and musket era.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In Chef de bataillon, battle is quick and dangerous. Created by the award-winning designers of Empire, Chef de bataillon is easy to learn, fast moving, and exciting to play. In addition Chef de bataillon scenarios allow you to jump into battle right away!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Discover the challenge and excitement of true tactical warfare in the Napoleonic era. Discover the most original approach in miniatures wargaming. Discover Chef de bataillon - you can almost smell the powder smoke!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Chef de bataillon contains: &amp;#10;A 196 page rule set;&amp;#10;a set of 65 pages of ratings, data and scenarios;&amp;#10;20 quick reference charts; and&amp;#10;2 die cut counter sheets.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Chef de bataillon brings to life the capabilities of troops and weapons and the effects of terrain in a new and innovative way. But most importantly, Chef de bataillon places you at the head of the troops. You must provide the leadership!  You must master the art of war at the tactical level! You must find the bravery to lead your formation into the very mouths of the guns for victory and glory!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;(source: Emperor's press website)&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
